{"tid":278020,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷要求《FIFA》調低C.朗能力值！","createTime":"2017-06-10T06:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T03:53:55.000Z","uid":31314,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2906817f6a7ecfd63552694bee41211c7e0eacf","tid":278020,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"在現實中，C.朗拿度已經轉型為一個高效射手、入球機器，但在虛擬遊戲中，他依然是一個無所不能的超級角色。射門、突破、強壯、過人能力都是頂級，技術上沒有死角。<br />\n<br />\n　　近期足球遊戲《FIFA18》公佈了他們的宣傳片和封面，C.朗拿度成為了今年的封面代言人。而關於球員能力值的問題又引起了網民們的廣泛討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">有的球迷就認為，C.朗拿度的部分數值需要向下調整。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　《電訊報》引用網民留言：「經過近2-3年的觀察，很明顯他是有所下滑的。我不是說他的能力下降了，但我今季看了他的大部分比賽，這很清楚。<span style=\"color: red;\">現實中他哪裡有92的帶球步頻，也沒有91的突破能力值</span>。他依然是世界上最頂級的終結者和得分者沒錯，但我們對比看看列貝利與洛賓的帶球頻率，C.朗拿度肯定不應該有這麼高的數據，不是嗎？」"},{"pid":"c158db4763e2013d11da0a04473a9b8abbd0c91c","tid":278020,"uid":84392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"177aaa139e55394e6f791525857eb874994fbcb0","tid":278020,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b69cd5fd0448a88d43f5d08b7a2a79809059921","tid":278020,"uid":15236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要求fifa 調高 Siuma 的能力值</blockquote><br />\n講得好"},{"pid":"09ae0047abb6ab349db04e2959532bfc215c0aee","tid":278020,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要求fifa 調高 Siuma 的能力值</blockquote><br />\nea表示不能破壞遊戲平衡，所以只能給siuma 99能力值"},{"pid":"9a272bdb4bde92f938983abd78c220466b347993","tid":278020,"uid":404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"今年勁左反而要調 <br />\n<br />\n應該幫佢調特性個d先岩"},{"pid":"ad1304b7556bbcbe9a08f9c352ce099c7d6ecd1d","tid":278020,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年勁左反而要調 <br />\n<br />\n應該幫佢調特性個d先岩</blockquote><br />\nwork rate, shoot ac.,好多<br />\n但速度相關要下調"},{"pid":"aa64a0f56e5b2ac3d10e95e4a330c3cb391d74bd","tid":278020,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"fifa能力值一向對名聲，球隊實力有關<br />\n<br />\n好像依家朗尼"},{"pid":"abb09ed09342154fd36d62d3ae3276a10160137b","tid":278020,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fifa能力值一向對名聲，球隊實力有關<br />\n<br />\n好像依家朗尼</blockquote><br />\n朗尼好似今年仲有84，真係on9。世三雖然今年勁，但係上季頹完之後有咩可能唔會調低"},{"pid":"0914f30a23902b08ac4c2d8d800e47ff1dd86e7b","tid":278020,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"fifa開始要加入個人屬性<br />\n好似機戰咁"},{"pid":"7d6073e1b61a6badd3fe2a2e85aa1caa1aa5e43f","tid":278020,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"fifia唔整勁d邊有咁多傻西成日讚c朗最強"},{"pid":"846d898116c9d17ae266af855ca9b370a9af3a29","tid":278020,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fifia唔整勁d邊有咁多傻西成日讚c朗最強</blockquote><br />\nfifa成日set到皇馬同c朗開外掛"},{"pid":"fb5b95142bbe6883754b93d4ba6f4f431d0360ee","tid":278020,"uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今年勁左反而要調 <br />\n<br />\n應該幫佢調特性個d先岩</blockquote><br />\nwork rate, shoot ac.,好多<br />\n但速度相關要下調</blockquote><br />\n但有統計今年呀朗平均top speed 快過上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n30&gt;32咁上下"},{"pid":"8dfddad282676a7abb6521d5e01cf457ab672f7d","tid":278020,"uid":30808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"咁美斯體力 十二碼<br />\nposition 呢d都要set低啦<br />\n散步帝點喺fifa生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae09ec2670c5bdbc278770711cfadb41a4076372","tid":278020,"uid":46151,"like":0,"disli